# ðŸ”§ Install

### Pip

```console
pip install stalcraft-api --upgrade
```

<details>
<summary>Manual</summary>

```console
git clone git@github.com:onejeuu/stalcraft-api.git
```

```console
cd stalcraft-api
```

```console
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
